    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Article in Look Magazine",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "current issue",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] Dept. of the",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Army, telephoned and advised he is checking on the article in the current",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "issue of Look Magazine by Dick Wilson, Editor of the Washington Bureau",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "of Look.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "He stated that in the opening part of the article he refers to the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "FBI and subsequent information is quoted coming from some branch of Naval",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Research. He stated the information reportedly coming from the Naval Research",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "section was not cleared through proper official channels. He stated he will",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "subsequently discuss the material with Dick Wilson in view of the fact the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "article contains many glaring errors.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] would appreciate it if the Bureau would advise him",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "if Mr. Wilson contacted the Bureau with reference to the part of the article",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "referring to the FBI. He observed that the reference to the FBI is somewhat",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "misleading.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "It will be recalled Captain Long secured a quote from the Bureau",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "in connection with the subject flying saucers. Captain Long was doing",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "research in that field at the time in view of the concern of the Dept.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "of the Navy over the publication of wholly misleading and inaccurate",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "articles on the subject of flying saucers.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "SJT:do",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "[unclear] never contacted FBI",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "but Dr Liddell did come",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
